@startuml spec-lifecycle-states
title AKDB Agent-Authoring - Spec Lifecycle States
[*] --> draft
draft : author sections; attach UML (spec_realizes_uml)
draft : map elements -> files (element_maps_to_file)
draft --> draft : edit / add diagram / map file
draft --> ready : set_spec_status(ready) [spec_validate blocking == empty]
ready --> draft : validate regresses (missing diagram / unresolved file-map)
ready : architecture complete; every core element pinned to a real file
ready --> implemented : code landed for the file-map targets
implemented --> superseded : a later spec supersedes this one
ready --> superseded : superseded before implementation
draft --> superseded : abandoned
superseded --> [*]
@enduml
